===Etymology===
Old High German ''miluh'', akin to Old Saxon ''miluk''

===Noun===
'''Milch''' {{f}}

# [[milk|Milk]]
# [[white|White]] [[fluid]] that is [[exuded]] by certain [[plants]]
# A [[white]] [[liquid]] that is a [[mixture]] of other [[substances]], where one of the components is very finely distributed
# [[semen|Semen]] of male [[fish]]

